{
  "ComponentID": "TC8871",
  "ComponentType": "Mono Audio Power Amplifier (Class AB/D Selectable)",
  "Description": "The TC8871 is a single-channel, 5W audio power amplifier designed for portable and low-voltage audio systems. It features selectable Class AB or Class D operation to balance efficiency and audio quality, with built-in feedback resistors that simplify external circuitry by eliminating the need for output coupling capacitors, bootstrap capacitors, or snubber networks. Operating from a 2.0V to 5.5V supply, it offers high power output (e.g., 5W into 2Ω at 5V), includes a shutdown mode for low power consumption, and integrates thermal shutdown protection. Its design minimizes FM interference and is suitable for applications like USB-powered speakers, laptops, and multimedia audio systems.",
